{"tid":143294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[移民啦屌]原來台中190萬買到500呎市區新樓","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T16:20:11.000Z","uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d002fa8cf90e687f1bb9fed4e409b78919836fe1","tid":143294,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5H9i35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5H9i35.jpg&h=d3421cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/212423_b14f5a6f86e3739747e7d847eb1a387d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F212423_b14f5a6f86e3739747e7d847eb1a387d.jpg&h=896af680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13.8坪x33.5=490呎<br />\n758/4= hkd189萬<br />\n5.8年樓<br />\n管理費1480/4= hkd 370蚊<br />\n<br />\ncheck黎google <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJ87Y4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJ87Y4N.jpg&h=efa7ec82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台中多數用電單車<br />\n8分鐘到中心商業區 行路22分鐘<br />\n當果度係老銅<br />\n樓位置～大坑 天后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上只係是但搵個例子<br />\n發現台灣係台北比較貴d<br />\n其他地方對香港人黎講簡直超值抵買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b9701b94264fe95e4aed93dd6b3107aa74760e","tid":143294,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一坪係35.5平方呎<br />\n唔係33.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d335a3d568607bebe72c879334cb22725b8fc63c","tid":143294,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"以台灣人收入來講算貴"},{"pid":"717c937b25ffc8c152c0427787c3b198d5f34823","tid":143294,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply